messages.message: @Jessica I investigated again, and copying a file with the same filename as another file in another folder will overwrite the file in folder 2 with the file from folder 1. you can reproduce the error here (https://uat.dogfood.instabase.com/felicia/my-repo/fs/Instabase%20Drive/copy_files_bug/#) by copying file `folder_1/file_2.txt` to `folder_2`  and check the content. `folder_1/file_2.txt` says `this is from folder 1` , original `folder_2/file_2.txt` says `this is from folder 2`
